    ("Agencia Libre NFL 2023: Todos los movimientos del día 14 de marzo; Jets, Cowboys, Giants... - AS USA Latino", "google-news", "Google News", "AS USA Latino", "Aún falta un día para que inicie oficialmente la agencia libre de la temporada 2023 de la NFL y la mayoría de los equipos han aprovechado la ventana previa para realizar negociaciones. Entre las grandes noticias está aquella en la que el quarterback Aaron Rodgers dará un gran anunció mañana a las 13:00 ET en el ‘The Pat McAfee Show’, además de una lista de demandas que pidió a los Jets parar llegar a New York. Aquí están los acuerdos reportados más destacados en el día en torno a la NFL y su agencia libre.", "La gerencia de los New York Jets le está cumpliendo los deseos de Aarón Rodgers con la incorporación de Allen Lazard. El wide receiver aceptó jugar con los Jets por los próximos cuatro años a cambio de 44 millones de dólares, según múltiples reportes. La llegada de Lazard a la Gran Manzana lo reunirá con el coordinador ofensivo Nathaniel Hackett, con el que coincidió durante dos temporadas en Green Bay.", 1, "sports", "2023-03-15T03:41:24Z", "https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMibWh0dHBzOi8vdXMuYXMuY29tL25mbC9hZ2VuY2lhLWxpYnJlLW5mbC0yMDIzLXRvZG9zLWxvcy1tb3ZpbWllbnRvcy1kZWwtZGlhLTE0LWRlLW1hcnpvLWpldHMtY293Ym95cy1naWFudHMtbi_SAXxodHRwczovL3VzLmFzLmNvbS9uZmwvYWdlbmNpYS1saWJyZS1uZmwtMjAyMy10b2Rvcy1sb3MtbW92aW1pZW50b3MtZGVsLWRpYS0xNC1kZS1tYXJ6by1qZXRzLWNvd2JveXMtZ2lhbnRzLW4vP291dHB1dFR5cGU9YW1w?oc=5", "https://img.asmedia.epimg.net/resizer/RCp09K4jEqaJg6Mw-ceMPpgK5B4=/1288x725/filters:focal(883x282:893x292)/cloudfront-eu-central-1.images.arcpublishing.com/diarioas/ITM73PO7YZEZJAN6KXLRRHV6LM.jpeg"),
    ("NCAA Tournament 2023 bracket: Computer simulation shares surprising upsets, March Madness picks, top sleepers - CBS Sports", "google-news", "Google News", "CBS Sports", "The 2023 NCAA Tournament bracket officially begins with the First Round beginning on Thursday at sites across the country. While plenty of attention will be on No. 1 seeds Alabama, Houston, Kansas and Purdue, this year's No. 2 seeds will also feel like national championship contenders during a year where parity reigned supreme in college basketball. Last season, there were a pair of No. 2 seeds that advanced to the Final Four, and Marquette, Texas, Arizona and UCLA all have the pedigree to make a run in the 2023 March Madness bracket.", "The SportsLine Projection Model simulated the entire 2023 NCAA Tournament 10,000 times. It has absolutely crushed its March Madness picks, beating over 92% of all CBS Sports brackets two of the last four tournaments. The model also nailed three teams in the West and South Region Sweet 16 last year, including No. 5 seed Houston.", 1, "sports", "2023-03-15T03:58:10Z", "https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMinQFodHRwczovL3d3dy5jYnNzcG9ydHMuY29tL2NvbGxlZ2UtYmFza2V0YmFsbC9uZXdzL25jYWEtdG91cm5hbWVudC0yMDIzLWJyYWNrZXQtY29tcHV0ZXItc2ltdWxhdGlvbi1zaGFyZXMtc3VycHJpc2luZy11cHNldHMtbWFyY2gtbWFkbmVzcy1waWNrcy10b3Atc2xlZXBlcnMv0gEA?oc=5", "https://sportshub.cbsistatic.com/i/r/2023/03/15/1b1265f1-8ff2-4287-abed-3e0468cb9bb3/thumbnail/770x433/1c991f6082676f9a6fb8bba1b5bac179/usatsi-boogie-ellis-usc.jpg"),
    ("Sergio Perez wins the Saudi Arabian Grand Prix, leading home another Red Bull one-two - CNN", "cnn", "CNN", "Issy Ronald", "Sergio Perez took an assured victory at the Saudi Arabian Grand Prix on Sunday, ahead of his teammate Max Verstappen, as Red Bull reaffirmed its dominance over their Formula One competitors with a second successive one-two of the season.", "Perez began the race in pole position and fought off a challenge from Aston Martin’s Fernando Alonso who briefly took the race lead at the first corner before the Mexican reclaimed his position by the fourth lap.",1,"sports","2023-03-15T03:58:10Z","https://edition.cnn.com/2023/03/19/motorsport/sergio-perez-saudi-arabia-grand-prix-spt-intl","https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/230319150314-07-saudi-arabia-grand-prix-2023.jpg?c=16x9&q=h_720,w_1280,c_fill/f_webp"),
